AddressInfo.Title: Almalomb
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Look for Almalomb restaurant and apartments

Connections.Comments: The charging fee is 100 HUF/kWh. Charging can be started in the Mobiliti app or with Mobiliti RFID. If you would like to report a problem, please click the yellow Report button on the profile of the charging station and fill in the form that appears!  Almalomb Restaurant and Almalomb Apartments provide two electric car charging station for its customers – just contact the reception for free complimentary access! The car charging stations are available 24/7 also for non-staying customers – in this case according to the Mobiliti.hu price list and conditions.  Enjoy your stay in our peaceful facilities, while doing a small thing to save the environment! We look forward to your bookings at almalomb.hu
